{"tid":1965272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［攬炒巴請入！］我地宜家再次全球眾籌，往支那死裡打！","createTime":"2020-04-09T11:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T10:00:05.000Z","uid":209516,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e7e1fce2a595581d06696305c5ea19dd9d9429","tid":1965272,"uid":209516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:06:34.000Z","msg":"宜家國際風向一面倒咁屌打緊匪共，我地香港人竟然宜家先黎收皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撐左咁多月，無可能唔繼續進擊<br />\n<br />\n日本同台灣係度say hi say thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英國話要審視華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n侵侵質問中國記者到仆街<br />\n連巴西、義大利都屌鳩中共，我地唔係唔做嘢呀嘛～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地只要大字寫<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Never Trust the CCP</span></strong><br />\n可能再加少少內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩假口罩等等<br />\n<br />\n跟住 最熟悉中共的香港人謹啟<br />\n<br />\n保證一定會Make 到noise！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n趁支那病，我地要更加落力打<br />\n怕傳染唔出街，眾籌會唔會得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然明白香港人宜家生活都好慘淡，所以希望有能力者可以加入幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果成事嘅話，我會將港共派個1 萬蚊預先捐5千出黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以幫手推比攬炒巴見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人頂著！我地一定要比中共更長命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3227ef18cc98ddb986f170ade949b1c392c324c","tid":1965272,"uid":209516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s